query: SELECT si.id, si.saleId, si.productId, si.quantity, si.unitPrice, si.subtotal, p.name as productName, s.saleNumber, s.total FROM saleItems si LEFT JOIN products p ON si.productId = p.id LEFT JOIN sales s ON si.saleId = s.id ORDER BY si.createdAt DESC LIMIT 10
